ak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5387, "text": "y de su c\u00f3nyuge, y de su hermano,"}, {"id": 260897, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 227, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5388, "text": "y de todos sus parientes que le acogieron,"}, {"id": 260898, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 227, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5389, "text": "y de cuantos viven en la tierra \u2013con tal de salvarse."}, {"id": 260899, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 227, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5390,