me": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5403, "text": "pues, ciertamente, del castigo de su Sustentador nadie hay que pueda sentirse [completamente] a salvo;"}, {"id": 260913, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5404, "text": "y que guardan su castidad,"}, {"id": 260914, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5405, "text": "[no cediendo a sus deseos] salvo con sus c\u00f3nyuges \u2013o sea, los que son leg\u00edtimamente suyos [por matrimonio]-- : pues en tal caso, est\u00e1n ciertamente libres de reproche,"}, {"id": 260915, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5406, "text": "pero los que pretenden exceder ese [l\u00edmite] --\u00e9sos, precisamente, son los transgresores;"}, {"id": 260916, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5407, "text": "y los que son fieles a la confianza depositada en ellos y a sus compromisos;"}, {"id": 260917, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5408, "text": "y los que, cuando dan testimonio, se mantienen firmes;"}, {"id": 260918, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5409, "text": "y los que observan fielmente sus oraciones."}, {"id": 260919, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5410, "text": "\u00a1\u00c9stos son los que morar\u00e1n con honor en los jardines [del para\u00edso]!"}, {"id": 260920, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 503, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5411, "text": "\u00bfQU\u00c9 LES PASA, pues, a los que se empe\