"ayah_number": 5414, "text": "\u00a1Nunca! \u00a1Pues, ciertamente, les hemos creado de algo que conocen [perfectamente]!"}, {"id": 260924, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 570, "ruku": 503, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5415, "text": "\u00a1Pues no! \u00a1Juro por el Sustentador de todos los ortos y los ocasos del sol: en verdad, somos capaces"}, {"id": 260925, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 570, "ruku": 503, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5416, "text": "de sustituirles por [gentes] mejores que ellos; pues nada hay que Nos impida [hacer Nuestra voluntad]!"}, {"id": 260926, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 570, "ruku": 503, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5417, "text": "D\u00e9jales, pues, con sus conversaciones fr\u00edvolas y sus juegos [de palabras] hasta que se encuentren con ese D\u00eda [del Juicio] que les ha sido prometido \u2013"}, {"id": 260927, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 570, "ruku": 503, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5418, "text": "el D\u00eda en que salgan precipitadamente de sus tumbas, como corriendo hacia una meta,"}, {"id": 260928, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 570, "ruku": 503, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5419, "text": "abatida la mirada, abrumados por la humillaci\u00f3n: ese D\u00eda que les fue prometido una y otra vez...."}]